raw_meta_yaml:
schema_version: 1

context:
  name: mini-racer
  version: "0.14.0"

package:
  name: ${{ name|lower }}
  version: ${{ version }}

source:
  url: https://github.com/bpcreech/PyMiniRacer/archive/refs/tags/v${{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 51028ec0bb267abc4537bcb90dc5b236273cefde0566ca368bec09e362c4a477
  patches: 
    - if: osx
      then: 0001-Update-v8_build.py.patch
build:     
  number: 2
  script:
    - if: target_platform == "osx-arm64"
      then: 
       - just build-dll "--target-cpu=arm64"
    - if: target_platform == "linux-aarch64"
      then: 
       - just build-dll "--aarch64-musl-compat"  "--target-cpu=arm64"
    - if: build_platform == target_platform
      then: 
       - just build-dll
    - ${{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv --no-deps --no-build-isolation
  dynamic_linking:
    binary_relocation: ${{ false if osx else true }}


requirements:
  build:
    - if: build_platform != target_platform
      then:
        - python
        - cross-python_${{ target_platform }}
        - rust
    - ${{ compiler('c') }}
    - ${{ stdlib('c') }}
    - ${{ compiler("cxx") }}
    - if: not win
      then: pkg-config
    - just
    - uv

  host:
    - python
    - pip
    - httplib2 =0.22.0
    - packaging >=25.0
    - six
    - setuptools =80.9.0
    - types-setuptools >=80.9.0
    - wheel
    - just
    - rust
    - babel
    - mypy
  run:
    - python

tests:
  - python:
      imports:
        - py_mini_racer
        - py_mini_racer._mini_racer
      pip_check: true
  - script:
      - python -c "from py_mini_racer import MiniRacer; ctx = MiniRacer(); print(ctx.eval('1+1'))"

about:
  summary: Minimal, modern embedded V8 for Python.
  license: ISC
  license_file:
    - LICENSE
    - library_licenses/
  homepage: https://github.com/bpcreech/PyMiniRacer
  repository: https://github.com/bpcreech/PyMiniRacer

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - HeavyTony2
